      "comment": "NOZOMU (3) is a two-year-old colt having his first run for the Daiki Chujo stable. Hasn't raced since finishing third over 1200m at the Gold Coast last December. Fitter after a trial win at the Gold Coast Poly and looks well placed. Can get off the mark with race experience on his side. DANCING BY (6) Written By filly from Surooj on debut for the Campton yard. Ran fourth in her latest trial at the Gold Coast Poly over 1050m. Can measure up. ACQUA ROMANE (1) is a Dirty Work gelding out of Biagiotti on debut for the Todd Payne yard. Ran fourth in a trial at Gosford over 800m. Lugging bit goes on and gets his chance from the inside gate. AIRBORNE AFFAIR (2) is a Trapeze Artist colt from She's My Girl on debut from the Ben Hull stable. Looks ready to go after a Beaudesert trial win. Top-three chance.",
